reviewText: Really uplifting cover. I haven't watched it yet...mostly bought it for the cover. I shall report back when I do...I'm sure it's a bunch of sexy butts to great classical music. Erotic art is always benefited when scored or provided a score of great orchestrations.

Dont bother with this one or any others from these guys.

Crap music sound track over the top and the camera work is appaling.
As soon as something is looking good the guy seems to want to annoy the viewer by moving away or just movig arround so fast you can not see anything.

Save your money and get one of the "gone wild" dvds. Much better and hotter content.
